-- Veolia Says Company, Some Managers Face Class Action in U.S.
-- B y   V i d y a   R o o t
-- 2012-01-06T08:02:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-06/veolia-says-company-some-managers-face-class-action-in-u-s-.html
Veolia Environnement SA (VIE)  said the
company and some of it former and current managers face a class
action lawsuit in the U.S., charging the company disemminated
misleading financial imformation between 2007 and 2011.  Veolia said the charges are “unfounded” and that it will
file a motion to dismiss  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
